data.description: RUTLAND GATE, IN THE MEADOWS.... Come home, relax and enjoy! Move-in quality, many renovations and great locale make this an exceptional find. You will appreciate the open kitchen, living room and more casual family room as your living choices. Kitchen has recent updates including wood cabinets, granite counters & newer appliances, plenty of storage cabinets. Stylish master bedroom with French doors to lanai & garden, dressing area with large "organized" master closet & updated master bath. Spacious 2nd and 3rd bedrooms. Other features include, plantation shutters, 2 linen closets, French doors, water heater 2016, AC in 2012, recent paint inside & out, crown moldings, interior doors & front windows replaced. Take advantage of the oversized garage with work bench & built-in storage. The utility room is 11x9 so there is room for an office plus more built-in storage cabinets. Pretty cul-de-sac lot with many fruit trees; lemon, lime, mango and grapefruit. Large lanai w/ covered area & heated pool. Enjoy the many amenities offered by the Meadows Community; town center, walking trails, lush landscaping & pretty lakes. Play golf at the Country Club or join for fitness, active tennis, clubhouse and huge pool. Convenient to downtown Sarasota, UTC & beaches.
